Ing '''Rutaceae''', a keraklan ausan dang familiang [[citrus]]<ref>http://www.plantsystematics.org/taxpage/0/family/Rutaceae.html</ref>, metung yang [[:en:family (biology)|familia]] da reng [[tanaman]], a keraklan bibili da king [[:en:order (biology)|orden]] [[Sapindales]]. 

Deng species king familiang iti maki sampaga lang mapipitna kareng apat o limang dake, a keraklan masikan a bau. Miayaliwa la dagul, manibat kareng [[dikut]] paras kareng [[palungpung]] ampong mangalating [[pun dutung]]. 

Ing pekamaulagang genus ning familia ya pin ing ''[[Citrus]]'', nung nu la kayabe deng [[:en:Orange (fruit)|dalandan]] (''C. sinensis''), [[limon]] (''C.'' × ''limon''), [[sua]] (''C. paradisi''), ampong [[Lime (fruit)|dalayap]] (miayaliwa, keraklan ''C. aurantifolia'', ing [[:en:key lime|key lime]]). Ing ''[[Boronia]]'' metung yang genus a Australiano, nung nu deng aliwa misna lang banglu sampaga a magagamit a kareng pisasali dang ''essential [[:en:Essential oil|oil]]''. Kayanib la murin keti deng genus a ''[[Zanthoxylum]]'' ampong ''[[Agathosma]]''.

